@YueLinHo I have already change rebase in [progit2-zh](https://github.com/progit/progit2-zh) by [change all "衍合" to "变基" by networm · Pull Request #85 · progit/progit2-zh](https://github.com/progit/progit2-zh/pull/85) and merged in.
My problem is to update the [ProGit v1](http://git-scm.com/book/zh/v1). I didn't want the wrong translation still exist in ProGit v1.

简单地说就是不能让第一版错误的“衍合”翻译误导其他人了；第二版翻译完成之前第一版都会存在，所以也需要修正这个问题。

